<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbd0352b1-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1971—<ref href="/us/pl/92/143">Pub. L. 92–143</ref> inserted “completion of the ginning season, but not later than the”.</p>
